      <span class="fg-kicker">Your Stack</span>
      <h2 class="fg-heading">The Focus & Attention Stack</h2>
      <p class="fg-body-muted">Built from proven basics. Start small, notice, then personalize.</p>

      <div class="fg-stack-grid">
        {%- comment -%} Card 1: L-Theanine + Caffeine {%- endcomment -%}
